data.description: Welcome to this exquisite D.R. Horton home, showcasing the Murval floor plan, in the heart of Tuscan Lakes. Boasting 4 bedrooms, and 3.5 baths, this home is as impressive as it is functional. As you step inside, you'll find a versatile study that's perfect for a home office. Upstairs, a game room offers endless possibilities for leisure and fun. The open concept effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a harmonious flow that's perfect for entertaining. The heart of this home lies in its expansive kitchen, which features granite countertops, 42" cabinets, ample storage space, counters for meal prep, and a breakfast bar. Step outside and envision a relaxing evening or a delightful weekend barbecue. The absence of rear neighbors enhances the tranquility of your living experience. Conveniently located near I-45, Galveston, Lago Mar, Tanger Outlets, Baybrook, and the Great Wolf Lodge Resort (2024). Don't wait! Schedule your private showing today.
